  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg px-3 py-2 inline-block self-start mb-4"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/xckefgqnh/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ProBall_Logo.jpg" alt="ProBall" class="h-8 w-auto object-contain"/></div>
      <p class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Developing the next generation of Australian basketball talent through elite coaching, structured development, and a love for the game.</p>
      <div class="flex space-x-3">
        <a href="http://www.facebook.com/proballaustralia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#004aad] flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary transition-colors" aria-label="ProBall on Facebook"><svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg></a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/proball_basketball/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#004aad] flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary transition-colors" aria-label="ProBall on Instagram"><svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Quick Links</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><a href="locations.html"  class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Programs &amp; Locations</a></li>
          <li><a href="schedule.html"   class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Schedule</a></li>
          <li><a href="blog/index.html" class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="how-to-join.html#register" class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">How to Join</a></li>
          <li><a href="team.html"       class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Our Team</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Contact</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><a href="tel:0406974582" class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">0406 974 582</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:info@proball.com" class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">info@proball.com</a></li>
          <li><a href="terms.html" class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Stay in the Loop</h5>
      <p class="font-body-md text-sm text-slate-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Get trial dates, season openings, and coaching tips straight to your inbox.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email address" class="bg-[#004aad] border-none rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary w-full placeholder-slate-500 outline-none"/>
        <button class="bg-primary text-on-primary p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors flex-shrink-0"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">send</span></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[#004aad] text-center">
    <p class="font-body-md text-xs text-slate-500">© 2025 ProBall. All rights reserved. Sydney's youth basketball program.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
